subject: Dear Sir
body:
Dear Sir
How are you doing today?Hope you are doing well
I have a business proposal that may interest you.
kindly reply back so that i will send your further details about the proposal.
waiting for your urgent response
Regards
Helen Opoku

subject: Re: Dear Sir
body:
Hello Helen,

Thank you for reaching out with your business proposal. I am interested in learning more about it. Could you please provide me with further details regarding the proposal? I look forward to hearing from you soon.

Best wishes,
Jae
